                <h1>Discovering Darwin: Evolution & Natural Selection Explained</h1>
                <p>Charles Darwin, a renowned naturalist, developed the theory of evolution through natural selection. His groundbreaking work, "On the Origin of Species," challenged traditional views on species creation. His ideas laid the foundation for modern biology, influencing various fields and reshaping our understanding of life on Earth.</p>
